    "description": "踏入一个世界，其中实时流媒体化为噩梦。成为一名不知不觉地踏入废弃疯人院的主播，只会陷入无法想象且无情的恐怖中。现实扭曲并变冷，谜团展开，将您的直播变成了可怕的下降。你准备好面对等待着的恐惧吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/03bbc47d0b5a20802940d910c830d39a.poster.avif?t=1717800136\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/03bbc47d0b5a20802940d910c830d39a.webm?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/03bbc47d0b5a20802940d910c830d39a.mp4?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌌 现实的崩溃：您的流媒体成为未知的通道，模糊了令人毛骨悚然的谜团和您自己的现实之间的界限。<br><br>🎮 沉浸式探索：穿越精心设计的环境，从破败的病房到充满谜团的房间，每一步都揭示出恐惧的层面。<br><br>🔍 神秘的谜题：解开谜一般的谜题，揭示疯人院可怕的历史和潜伏其中的邪恶力量。<br><br>👻 与鬼魂的互动：与备受折磨的灵魂建立联系，每次相遇都会改变你的命运和他们的命运。<br><br>💀 揭示实体：深入黑暗，揭示一个邪恶的存在，操纵失落的灵魂变成复仇的幽灵。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/44088933cf20b2aef7865a7fde8e6703.poster.avif?t=1717800136\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/44088933cf20b2aef7865a7fde8e6703.webm?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/44088933cf20b2aef7865a7fde8e6703.mp4?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沉浸于心理恐怖和动态叙述之中，每一次选择都会塑造你的命运。你能重写这个噩梦般故事的结局吗？<br><br>准备迎接前所未有的直播：《疯人院疯狂》吸引着你，模糊了娱乐和恐怖之间的界限。你有勇气面对黑暗中潜伏的事物吗？准备好，因为你的现实即将破裂。&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/fd5314709bbdfb716e6667eab6b969b2.poster.avif?t=1717800136\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/fd5314709bbdfb716e6667eab6b969b2.webm?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358420/extras/fd5314709bbdfb716e6667eab6b969b2.mp4?t=1717800136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
